  <description>
    <p>
      <em>
      </em>SlimeVR<em>
    </em> is a set of open hardware sensors and open source software that facilitates full-body tracking (FBT) in virtual reality. With no base station required, SlimeVR makes wireless VR FBT affordable and comfortable.
